      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>כְּגוֹן שֶׁנְּטָלָהּ לָמוֹד בָּהּ, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba bar Naḥmani, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2581\" data-full-name=\"Rabba bar Naḥmani\" data-name-he=\"רַבָּה בַּר נַחְמָנִי\">וְכִדְרַבָּה</span> – דְּאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba bar Naḥmani, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2581\" data-full-name=\"Rabba bar Naḥmani\" data-name-he=\"רַבָּה בַּר נַחְמָנִי\">רַבָּה</span>: הִכִּישָׁהּ –",
