    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַאי גַּוְנָא מִי אָמַר?! <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֶלָּא אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rava, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2582\" data-full-name=\"Rava\" data-name-he=\"רָבָא\">רָבָא</span>: אֲנִי וַאֲרִי",
