        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁבַּחֲבוּרָה תַּרְגֵּימְנוּהָ – וּמַנּוּ? <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Zeira I, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1017\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Zeira I\" data-name-he=\"רַבִּי זֵירָא א׳\" data-resolution-rule=\"default_early_context\" data-resolution-explanation=\"Defaulted to the earlier figure because no later-context cue appeared nearby.\" data-resolution-reasons=\"[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heuristic&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;Default early context&quot;,&quot;detail&quot;:&quot;Defaulted to the earlier figure because no later-context cue appeared nearby.&quot;,&quot;attribution&quot;:&quot;Girsology disambiguation heuristics&quot;}]\">רַבִּי זֵירָא</span>; הָכָא בְּמַאי עָסְקִינַן –",
