      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-authority-id=\"2763\" data-full-name=\"Shmuel II\" data-name-he=\"שמואל\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Shmuel II, first-generation Amora\">שְׁמוּאֵל</span>: <span class=\"ein_mishpat_marker\" data-ein-mishpat-id=\"3\" data-marker-letter=\"ד\">ד</span>הַנּוֹטֵל כְּלִי מִן הָאוּמָּן לְבַקְּרוֹ, וְנֶאֱנַס בְּיָדוֹ –",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "חַיָּיב. וְהָנֵי מִילֵּי הוּא דְּקַיְצִי <span class=\"ein_mishpat_marker\" data-ein-mishpat-id=\"4\" data-marker-letter=\"ה\">ה</span>דְּמֵיהּ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">☆</span>הַהוּא",
